descCRN[30385] = '<p>*First day attendance required*<br/>Primarily designed to improve oral communication and to strengthen the student\'s written proficiency and his or her awareness of grammar intricacies.  In relation to writing, it serves as a bridge to upper-level courses. Conversations and compositions are based on cultural and literary topics. Class activities vary according to the instructor but usually include five to fifteen minute presentations, interviews with native speakers, commentary on videos and movies, short stories, plays and short novels, writing strategies, and self-correction exercises. It often involves extensive reading appropriate to the level. (4 credits)</p>';
